                    --- CAEN SpA - Software Division ---

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    CAEN A5818 Driver

    Install procedure on Linux.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


Prerequisites
-------------

- Linux kernel
  Compilation tested on:
  - Debian: 11, 12, 13
  - Ubuntu (including HWE): 16.04, 18.04, 20.04, 22.04, 24.04
  - RHEL (and derivatives): 7.9, 8.10, 9.7, 10.1
  - Fedora: 42, 43
- dkms


Install
-------

In the extracted folder run

    $ sudo ./install.sh
